      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katonah%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The John Jay Homestead, once home to the first U.S. Supreme Court Chief Justice, is also a National Historic Landmark.",
